<Link id="l00237" /><CodeLine lineNumber="237"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Non-owning SymbolStringPool entry pointer. Instances are comparable with</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00238" /><CodeLine lineNumber="238"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// SymbolStringPtr instances and guaranteed to have the same hash, but do not</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00239" /><CodeLine lineNumber="239"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// affect the ref-count of the pooled string (and are therefore cheaper to</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00240" /><CodeLine lineNumber="240"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// copy).</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00241" /><CodeLine lineNumber="241"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00242" /><CodeLine lineNumber="242"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// NonOwningSymbolStringPtrs are silently invalidated if the pool entry&#39;s</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00243" /><CodeLine lineNumber="243"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// ref-count drops to zero, so they should only be used in contexts where a</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00244" /><CodeLine lineNumber="244"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// corresponding SymbolStringPtr is known to exist (which will guarantee that</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00245" /><CodeLine lineNumber="245"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// the ref-count stays above zero). E.g. in a graph where nodes are</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00246" /><CodeLine lineNumber="246"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// represented by SymbolStringPtrs the edges can be represented by pairs of</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00247" /><CodeLine lineNumber="247"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// NonOwningSymbolStringPtrs and this will make the introduction of deletion</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00248" /><CodeLine lineNumber="248"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// of edges cheaper.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00249" /><CodeLine lineNumber="249" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/nonowningsymbolstringptr"><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">class </span><span class="doxyHighlight"><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/nonowningsymbolstringptr/#a1b07b73c4b416133b5a40b5d275f1fdb">NonOwningSymbolStringPtr</a> : </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">public</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/symbolstringptrbase/#a334e27918886db7a1a9e3ac95e34d569">SymbolStringPtrBase</a> &#123;</span></CodeLine>
